-- Old Mutual `On Track' to Reach 2012 Cost Saving Targets, CEO Roberts Says
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-08-06T06:44:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/old-mutual-on-track-to-reach-2012-cost-saving-targets-ceo-roberts-says.html

          
          
             Old Mutual Plc is “on track” to
achieve its cost savings targets for 2012, Chief Executive
Officer Julian Roberts said on a conference call with reporters
today.  
 All of the company’s units are within range of return on
equity targets for 2012, he said.  
          
          


  


        